"\t\t<td><notr>&Pi;&omicron;&tau;&alpha;&mu;&#972;&sigmaf;</notr></td>\n"
"\t\t<td>the river Eridanus (Latin), an unnamed River (Greek);<br />here a river god is depicted</td>\n"
"\t\t<td><img width=\"255\" src=\"descr_pics/aratea_small_eri.jpg\"/></td>\n"
