"\t\t<td>The star in front of the dog <br /> mirrored depiction<br />(an asterism of three stars forming a small dog is already mentioned by Eratosthenes, but the name of the figure was always \"Prokyon\"). Procyon is a Greek term (with \"k\") latinized.</td>\n"
